Author Manuscript

Clerico et al.

Page 19
Highlights • Hsp70 molecular chaperones perform a wide array of functions using a simple
mechanism. • Key to the function of Hsp70s is how they recognize and influence their
substrates. • Hsp70s team with co-chaperones, which enhance functional diversity and
cellular roles. • Current understanding of Hsp70-substrate interactions is limited.

