Figure 3. Hsp70s can actively unfold misfolded states (M) and partner with other chaperones, like ClpB to undo aggregates (A). Hsp70s must bind to accessible binding sites to initiate the unfolding or disaggregation reaction. The coloring scheme is the same as in Figure 2.

